entry.title: Muslims Across Middle East Rally in Support of Palestinians
entry.content: Demonstrators from Lebanon to Iran expressed solidarity with Gaza and anger at Israel in a region at risk of a widening war.

entry.title: Gaza Residents Brace for Israeli Offensive After Evacuation Demand
entry.content: Residents of Gaza were bracing for a more powerful assault by the Israeli military, which on Friday demanded a mass evacuation of some of the territory’s most densely populated neighborhoods.

entry.title: Ukraine, Partners Fight to Avoid Stalemate as Headwinds Grow
entry.content: Concerns about the slow pace of Ukraine’s advances this year have been accentuated by doubts over the durability of Western aid.
